dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning for Price County, Wisconsin in 2013. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Price_Zoning_2013.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'A1_ZONING', 'C_1_ZONING', 'C_2_ZONING', 'C1_ZONING', 'C2_ZONING', 'CI1_ZONING', 'CIC_ZONING', 'I1_ZONING', 'I2_ZONING', 'R1_ZONING', 'R2_ZONING', 'R3_ZONING', 'RBR_ZONING', 'RF1_ZONING', 'RFC_ZONING', 'RR1_ZONING', 'SP1_ZONING', 'W_ZONING', and 'W1_ZONING'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
